<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557909>
    dc:description "FIGURES 97–102. Male genitalia, tegmen, group dispar: 97. Amblycerus crassipunctatus, 98. A. dispar, 99. A. insuturatus, 100. A. schwarzi, 101. A. taeniopygus and 102. Amblycerus goianiensis Santos & Ribeiro-Costa, sp. n. Scale bars = 0.25 mm." ;
