<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3557919>
    dc:description "FIGURES 117–118. FIGURE 117. Map with the geographical distribution of A. crassipunctatus and A. dispar. Leaked symbols refer to bibliography data. FIGURE 118. Map with the geographical distribution of A. insuturatus and A. schwarzi. Leaked symbols refer to bibliography data." ;
